---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Golfové ihrisko"
description: "9-jamkové ihriská GREEN MEADOWS a GREEN PARK v Ivanke pri Nitre. Driving range, putting green, chipping area."
permalink: /golfove-ihrisko/
---
<header class="header header--inner">
  <div class="text-box">
    <h1 class="heading-primary">
      <span class="heading-primary-main">Golfové ihrisko</span>
      <span class="heading-primary-sub">Green Meadows &amp; Green Park</span>
    </h1>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="page-content">
  <p style="background:#f0fff8;border-left:.4rem solid #28b485;padding:1.2rem 2rem;font-size:1.5rem;color:#015C39;margin-bottom:3rem;">
    <strong>2026:</strong> Ihriská GREEN MEADOWS a GREEN PARK sa striedajú — sledujte značenie pri vstupe do areálu.
  </p>

  <div class="course-cards">
    {% for course in collections.courses %}
    <a href="/golfove-ihrisko/{{ course.data.slug }}/" class="course-card">
      <img src="{{ course.data.hero_image }}" alt="{{ course.data.title }}" class="course-card__img" loading="lazy">
      <div class="course-card__body">
        <div class="course-card__title">{{ course.data.title }}</div>
        <ul class="course-card__features">
          {% for f in course.data.features | limit(5) %}
          <li>{{ f }}</li>
          {% endfor %}
        </ul>
      </div>
    </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>

  <h2>Čo nájdete v areáli</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Driving range 250 m — reálne fervejové odpalisko a podložky</li>
    <li>Patovací green — dva druhy tráv</li>
    <li>Chipping area 2× — tri čipovacie gríny</li>
    <li>Terasa pre firemné akcie a turnaje</li>
    <li>Turnajový ketering od bagety až po *****</li>
    <li>Team building od 20,- EUR/osoba</li>
  </ul>
</div>
